{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## SmartScreen Web Threats\r\n\r\nHunt for users browsing to malicious, phishing, tech-scam, untrusted, custom-blocked, or **adult / web-content-filter** sites surfaced by Microsoft Defender SmartScreen and Network Protection (Web Content Filtering).\r\n\r\nUse the **Time Range**, **User (UPN)**, **Device**, and **URL contains** filters to scope. Tabs further narrow the threat category. Start with *Top Users / Domains* for triage, then pivot into *Risky User Correlation* to find users that crossed from adult content into malicious activity."
      },
      "name": "header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "6cba59cc-7211-42de-ade8-13f364ee4107",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimePicker",
            "label": "Time Range",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                { "durationMs": 1800000 },
                { "durationMs": 3600000 },
                { "durationMs": 14400000 },
                { "durationMs": 43200000 },
                { "durationMs": 86400000 },
                { "durationMs": 259200000 },
                { "durationMs": 604800000 },
                { "durationMs": 1209600000 },
                { "durationMs": 2592000000 },
                { "durationMs": 5184000000 },
                { "durationMs": 7776000000 }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            },
            "timeContext": { "durationMs": 86400000 },
            "value": { "durationMs": 2592000000 }
          },
          {
            "id": "f1a1b8e1-1111-4111-aaaa-111111111111",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "UserUPN",
            "label": "User (Entra UPN)",
            "type": 2,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [ "value::all" ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "query": "DeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where isnotempty(InitiatingProcessAccountUpn)\r\n| distinct InitiatingProcessAccountUpn\r\n| order by InitiatingProcessAccountUpn asc\r\n| project value = InitiatingProcessAccountUpn, label = InitiatingProcessAccountUpn",
            "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
            "value": [ "value::all" ]
          },
          {
            "id": "f1a1b8e1-2222-4222-aaaa-222222222222",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "DeviceName",
            "label": "Device",
            "type": 2,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [ "value::all" ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "query": "DeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where isnotempty(DeviceName)\r\n| distinct DeviceName\r\n| order by DeviceName asc\r\n| project value = DeviceName, label = DeviceName",
            "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
            "queryType": 0,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
            "value": [ "value::all" ]
          },
          {
            "id": "f1a1b8e1-3333-4333-aaaa-333333333333",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "UrlContains",
            "label": "URL contains",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": false,
            "value": ""
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "parameters - 1"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          { "id": "tab-overview",    "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Top Users / Domains",       "subTarget": "Overview",  "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-correlate",   "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Risky User Correlation",    "subTarget": "Correlate", "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-all",         "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "All Categories (URL+Files)","subTarget": "First",     "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-webcat",      "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Web Content Filter (Adult/Category)", "subTarget": "WebCat", "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-files",       "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Files (SmartScreenApp)",    "subTarget": "Eighth",    "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-techscam",    "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "TechScam (URL)",            "subTarget": "Second",    "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-phishing",    "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Phishing (URL)",            "subTarget": "Third",     "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-untrusted",   "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Untrusted (URL)",           "subTarget": "Fourth",    "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-malicious",   "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Malicious (URL)",           "subTarget": "Fifth",     "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-customblock", "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Custom Block List (URL)",   "subTarget": "Sixth",     "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-custompol",   "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Custom Policy (URL)",       "subTarget": "Seventh",   "style": "link" }
        ]
      },
      "name": "links - 2"
    },

    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Top Users / Domains",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": { "json": "Top 25 users, devices, domains, and SmartScreen/Web-Content categories across the selected scope. Click a row to view the **same scope** filtered in the category tabs." },
            "name": "ovw-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let urlFilter = '{UrlContains}';\r\nDeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{DeviceName}') or DeviceName in ('{DeviceName}')\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{UserUPN}')   or InitiatingProcessAccountUpn in ('{UserUPN}')\r\n| where isempty(urlFilter) or RemoteUrl has urlFilter\r\n| extend P = parse_json(AdditionalFields)\r\n| extend Category    = tostring(P.Experience),\r\n         WebCategory = tostring(P.ResponseCategory)\r\n| extend Bucket = case(\r\n     ActionType == \"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\", strcat(\"WebContent: \", iff(isempty(WebCategory),\"(uncategorized)\",WebCategory)),\r\n     isnotempty(Category), Category,\r\n     ActionType)\r\n| summarize Events = count() by Bucket\r\n| top 20 by Events desc\r\n| render barchart",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Events by Category",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "ovw-category"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let urlFilter = '{UrlContains}';\r\nDeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{DeviceName}') or DeviceName in ('{DeviceName}')\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{UserUPN}')   or InitiatingProcessAccountUpn in ('{UserUPN}')\r\n| where isempty(urlFilter) or RemoteUrl has urlFilter\r\n| extend Domain = tolower(tostring(parse_url(RemoteUrl).Host))\r\n| where isnotempty(Domain)\r\n| summarize Hits = count(), Users = dcount(InitiatingProcessAccountUpn), Devices = dcount(DeviceName) by Domain\r\n| top 25 by Hits desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Top 25 Domains",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": { "rowLimit": 25 }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "ovw-domain"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let urlFilter = '{UrlContains}';\r\nDeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{DeviceName}') or DeviceName in ('{DeviceName}')\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{UserUPN}')   or InitiatingProcessAccountUpn in ('{UserUPN}')\r\n| where isempty(urlFilter) or RemoteUrl has urlFilter\r\n| extend P = parse_json(AdditionalFields)\r\n| extend Category = tostring(P.Experience), WebCategory = tostring(P.ResponseCategory)\r\n| summarize Hits = count(),\r\n            Devices = dcount(DeviceName),\r\n            Domains = dcount(tostring(parse_url(RemoteUrl).Host)),\r\n            MaliciousHits = countif(Category in (\"Malicious\",\"Phishing\",\"TechScam\")),\r\n            AdultHits     = countif(WebCategory has_any (\"Adult\",\"Pornography\",\"Nudity\",\"Sexually\",\"Mature\")),\r\n            LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated)\r\n         by User = InitiatingProcessAccountUpn\r\n| where isnotempty(User)\r\n| top 25 by Hits desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Top 25 Users (with Malicious & Adult counts)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "rowLimit": 25,
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "MaliciousHits", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "redBright" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "AdultHits",     "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "orange" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "Hits",          "formatter": 4, "formatOptions": { "palette": "blue" } }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "ovw-users"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": { "parameterName": "Tab", "comparison": "isEqualTo", "value": "Overview" },
      "name": "GroupOverview"
    },

    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Risky User Correlation",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": { "json": "Users who triggered **both** adult/risky web-content events **and** SmartScreen Malicious / Phishing / TechScam events in the selected window. These are prime candidates for SOC follow-up: a browsing path that started in adult / shady categories and ended in confirmed malicious destinations." },
            "name": "corr-text"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let urlFilter = '{UrlContains}';\r\nlet base =\r\nDeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{DeviceName}') or DeviceName in ('{DeviceName}')\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{UserUPN}')   or InitiatingProcessAccountUpn in ('{UserUPN}')\r\n| where isempty(urlFilter) or RemoteUrl has urlFilter\r\n| extend P = parse_json(AdditionalFields)\r\n| extend Category = tostring(P.Experience), WebCategory = tostring(P.ResponseCategory)\r\n| extend IsAdult     = WebCategory has_any (\"Adult\",\"Pornography\",\"Nudity\",\"Sexually\",\"Mature\",\"Gambling\",\"Dating\"),\r\n         IsMalicious = Category in (\"Malicious\",\"Phishing\",\"TechScam\");\r\nbase\r\n| summarize\r\n    AdultHits      = countif(IsAdult),\r\n    MaliciousHits  = countif(IsMalicious),\r\n    FirstAdult     = minif(TimeGenerated, IsAdult),\r\n    LastAdult      = maxif(TimeGenerated, IsAdult),\r\n    FirstMalicious = minif(TimeGenerated, IsMalicious),\r\n    LastMalicious  = maxif(TimeGenerated, IsMalicious),\r\n    Devices        = make_set(DeviceName, 10),\r\n    SampleAdultUrls     = make_set_if(RemoteUrl, IsAdult, 5),\r\n    SampleMaliciousUrls = make_set_if(RemoteUrl, IsMalicious, 5)\r\n  by User = InitiatingProcessAccountUpn\r\n| where isnotempty(User) and AdultHits > 0 and MaliciousHits > 0\r\n| extend MinutesAdultToMalicious = iff(isnotempty(FirstMalicious) and isnotempty(FirstAdult), datetime_diff('minute', FirstMalicious, FirstAdult), int(null))\r\n| order by MaliciousHits desc, AdultHits desc",
              "size": 2,
              "title": "Users with Adult+Malicious activity",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "rowLimit": 200,
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "MaliciousHits", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "redBright" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "AdultHits",     "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "orange" } }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "corr-grid"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let urlFilter = '{UrlContains}';\r\nDeviceEvents\r\n| where ActionType in (\"SmartScreenAppWarning\",\"SmartScreenUrlWarning\",\"ExploitGuardNetworkProtectionBlocked\")\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{DeviceName}') or DeviceName in ('{DeviceName}')\r\n| where \"*\" in ('{UserUPN}')   or InitiatingProcessAccountUpn in ('{UserUPN}')\r\n| where isempty(urlFilter) or RemoteUrl has urlFilter\r\n| extend P = parse_json(AdditionalFields)\r\n| extend Category = tostring(P.Experience), WebCategory = tostring(P.ResponseCategory)\r\n| extend Severity = case(\r\n     Category in (\"Malicious\",\"Phishing\",\"TechScam\"), \"High\",\r\n     WebCategory has_any (\"Adult\",\"Pornography\",\"Nudity\",\"Sexually\",\"Mature\"), \"Medium\",\r\n     Category in (\"Untrusted\",\"CustomBlockList\",\"CustomPolicy\"), \"Low\",\r\n     \"Info\")\r\n| project TimeGenerated, User = InitiatingProcessAccountUpn, DeviceName, Severity, Category, WebCategory, ActionType, RemoteUrl, FileName, InitiatingProcessFileName, InitiatingProcessCommandLine\r\n| order by TimeGenerated desc",
              "size": 2,
              "title": "Full event timeline (filtered)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimePicker",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "rowLimit": 2000,
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "Severity", "formatter": 11, "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "High",   "representation": "Critical", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Medium", "representation": "2",        "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Low",    "representation": "3",        "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "Default",                        "representation": "Info",     "text": "{0}{1}" }
                      ]
                  }}
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "corr-timeline"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": { "parameterName": "Tab", "comparison": "isEqualTo", "value": "Correlate" },
      "name": "GroupCorrelate"
    },

    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "All Categories",
        "items": [
          {
